snippet.title: Zombie Pinball - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
"Frankenstein and his buddies, zombies, werewolves, undead rockers, burning or dripping skeletons will make you sweat...

You will love ZOMBIE PINBALL"

That's a bold claim for a game with mixed user reviews on Steam.

Zombie Pinball (C) Shine Research
Published by Plug In Digital
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/458510/Zombie_Pinball/
Also available on Xbox One
